{"tid":488405,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[高鐵2.0] 料沙中線超支比高鐵153億元更多　田北辰：不希望成「千億鐵路」","createTime":"2017-12-03T16:30:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-06T08:58:52.000Z","uid":59491,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7464f42d14239d913c0a1b13415a53aba686857a","tid":488405,"uid":59491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T16:30:12.000Z","msg":"港鐵沙中線工程超支金額將於月內揭曉，港鐵表示將於聖誕節前後向政府提交沙中線最新造價估算數字。立法會鐵路事宜小組委員會主席田北辰出席商台節目時，預料因考古、工程成本上漲等原因，<span style=\"color: red;\">總超支額將高於高鐵超支的153億元。</span><br />\n<br />\n然而田北辰又表示，沙中線原先預料造價約800億，因此不希望總超支額會多於200億，否則沙中線會成為<span style=\"color: red;\">「千億鐵路」</span>，形容是<span style=\"color: red;\">「香港開埠以來都未聽過」</span>，相信立法會議員未來將要求港鐵為造價封頂。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171203/s00001/1512270451258\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171203%2Fs00001%2F1512270451258&d=FoUqEXIYCekD%2FWcRzGgbQ8KJ7zzy8RXHrd%2FDXtMH0Y8%3D&h=24d9cea8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171203%2Fs00001%2F1512270451258&h=9395ed63\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171203/s00001/1512270451258</a>"},{"pid":"ce7419238c4f118af52134b02abf8ca319b4ec01","tid":488405,"uid":155568,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T16:35:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c703be402b9a76eff8d81197cd8909f42bd8a0dd","tid":488405,"uid":155568,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T16:36:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"47f0aa35391b582c4d49ff3889b8a9f97d155249","tid":488405,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T16:46:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2e0d0cf0d6c367b0201a45065b820598731fa9a2","tid":488405,"uid":155534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T02:12:50.000Z","msg":"下，又過千億